thread.title_full: Spa Store Australia reviewed by Peter

author: Peter
title: Peter
text: I decided to try buying the part I needed from Spa Store rather than the manufacturer. It looked like the right one and they checked that it should fit before I decided to purchase. It was at least as good a quality as the old one that needed to be replaced, a little cheaper and I am sure it arrived more quickly as it was just travelling within NSW.
